			<div class="comment-avatar"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/c25ca283c52d1a6d900211afaafb939b?s=45&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-45 photo' height='45' width='45' /></div>
