			<div class="comment-content">
									
				<p>People make stupid assumptions. If I go to the store and buy a bunch of things some food and some not and I swipe my EBT card, others might assume I paid for everything with it. What really happens is the computer calculates the eligible food total only and charges that to the EBT card. Then I have to somehow pay for the rest some other way.</p>
