			<div class="comment-content">
									
				<p>it is society&#8217;s duty to help take care of each other, that is a big part of what is wrong us today!!!  We are a fend for yourself and who cares about anybody society&#8230;  We need to lose mentality and take care of each other&#8230;</p>
<p>As for you buying Panera Bread, it is not affordable for their own employees&#8230;  I worked there for 2 years and had to fight tooth and nail just to get $8.25/hour, and I was 27 years old with the usual bills&#8230;  Needless to say, I also worked a part time job to help supplement and still couldn&#8217;t afford to eat here&#8230;  I was hired fulltime, worked over my scheduled shift, came in on my day off, and came in early when needed</p>
