<p>He&#8217;s just showboating at this point&#8230;  When you only offer your GM&#8217;s insurance, pay your shift  manager&#8217;s that have worked for you for 6+ years barely $9/hour, and anybody below a shift manager, good luck getting a decent wage&#8230;  Panera Bread doesn&#8217;t like to give raises, and if you do find yourself lucky enough to receive a raise, it&#8217;s only $0.10</p>
